==English==

===Etymology===
Greek ''[[ακμή]]'', point, top, acne

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The top or highest point; the culmination.
#* The very '''acme''' and pitch of life for epic poetry. - [[w:Alexander Pope|Alexander Pope]]
#* The moment when a certain power reaches the '''acme''' of its supremacy. - [[w:I. Taylor|I. Taylor]]
# {{medicine}} The crisis or height of a disease.
# Mature age; full bloom of life. - [[w:Ben Jonson|Ben Jonson]]

